<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<!DOCTYPE document SYSTEM "rml_1_0.dtd">
<document filename="coppa_consent_request_email_attachment.pdf"
		  invariant="1"
		  compression="1"
		  title="COPPA Consent Request Form"
		  creator="NextThought"
		  author="NextThought">

<template pagesize="letter" leftMargin="72" showBoundary="0">
	<pageTemplate id="main" pagesize="(595,842)">
	<frame id="first" x1="1in" y1="4in" width="6in" height="7in"/>
	<frame id="second" x1="1in" y1="1in" width="4in" height="2.5in"/>
	<frame id="third" x1="5.5in" y1="1in" width="1.5in" height="2.5in"/>
	</pageTemplate>
</template>

<stylesheet>
	<paraStyle name="h1" fontName="Helvetica-Bold" fontSize="11" leading="12"/>
	<paraStyle name="h2" fontName="Helvetica-Bold" fontSize="11" leading="20" spaceBefore="12"/>
	<paraStyle name="normal" fontName="Helvetica" fontSize="11"
			   leading="12" spaceBefore="10"/>
	<paraStyle name="sendTo" leftIndent="0.5in" parent="normal"
			   spaceBefore="10" spaceAfter="2"/>
</stylesheet>

<story>
<img src="[nti.appserver]/templates/coppa_consent_header.png"
	   width="3.5in"
	   height="0.55in"
	   align="left"/>
<para style="h1" spaceBefore="12">
Please keep a copy of this form for your records.
</para>
<para style="normal">
Your child has expressed a desire to join NextThought, a social
learning platform that allows students to interact, communicate, and
collaborate with others within the content of their educational
materials.
</para>

<para style="normal">
Because your child is under 13 years of age, parental permission is
necessary before NextThought can collect any information that may
personally identify your child or allow access to its social features.
</para>

<para style="normal">
You may give your permission by completing and sending this form.
</para>

<para style="sendTo">
<b>By Mail:</b><br />
NextThought, LLC<br />
Attn: Compliance<br />
731-A Asp Avenue<br />
Norman, OK 73069
</para>
<para style="sendTo">
<b>By Fax:</b><br />
(405) 308-4310
</para>
<para style="sendTo">
<b>By Electronic Scan:</b><br />
compliance@nextthought.com
</para>

<para style="normal" spaceBefore="12">
After receiving consent NextThought will ask for your child's full
name, school, and email address. We may save your email address to
send you notice about changes to our Terms of Service or privacy
practices. If you wish to receive additional information from
NextThought, please indicate so below.
</para>

<para style="normal">
Please review the email accompanying this form and the
<a color="blue" href="https://docs.google.com/a/nextthought.com/document/pub?id=1kNo6hwwKwWdhq7jzczAysUWhnsP9RfckIet11pWPW6k">
Children's Privacy Policy
</a>
to learn more about NextThought's
information collection and sharing practices.
</para>

<para style="normal" backColor="#f2f2f2"
	  leftIndent="0.1in" rightIndent="0.1in"
	  leading="15"
	  spaceBefore="18"
	  borderWidth="1pt" borderColor="#000000"
	  borderPadding="8">
Child’s username: <b>${context/username}</b><br/>
Child’s first name: <b>${options/profile/realname}</b><br />
Parent’s email address: <b>${options/email}</b><br />

<font name="Helvetica-Bold" size="12">[ ]</font> Check here if you would like to receive notices from NextThought.
</para>

<nextFrame />

<hr width="80%" thickness="1" color="black" spaceBefore="30"
	spaceAfter="0"
	align="left"/>

<para style="normal" spaceBefore="0" spaceAfter="0">
Parent/Guardian Signature
</para>
<hr width="80%" thickness="1" color="black" spaceBefore="30"
	spaceAfter="0"
	align="left"/>

<para style="normal" spaceBefore="0" spaceAfter="0">
Parent/Guardian Name (Please Print)
</para>
<hr width="80%" thickness="1" color="black" spaceBefore="30"
	spaceAfter="0"
	align="left"/>

<para style="normal" spaceBefore="0" spaceAfter="0">
Parent's Telephone<br />
(We use this for confirmation purposes only.)
</para>

<nextFrame />
<hr width="60%" thickness="1" color="black" spaceBefore="0"
	spaceAfter="0"
	align="left"/>
<para style="normal" spaceBefore="1pt" spaceAfter="0" leading="0">
Date
</para>

</story>
